138
00:07:02,479 --> 00:07:10,639
The point is most people don't want to validate because if you validate it means you might invalidate your idea and most people it's an emotional thing.

139
00:07:10,639 --> 00:07:11,440
They don't want to.

140
00:07:11,440 --> 00:07:14,880
